title: Starstruck_1982_DiVX_AC3_Eng_Winman99.avi
description:
This is an Aussie version of your typical 1930's Mickey Rooney/Judy Garland film meets A HARD DAYS NIGHT from the Gillian Armstrong, director of such classics as MY BRILLIANT CAREER and MRS SOFFEL. Angus (Ross O'Donovan in a fantastic perfomence) is determined to make his big sister the pop star she wants to be. Parodies and satire of every rock/pop film ever abound with a fresh Aussie sense of humor and a very catchy original soundtrack make this a hard to find classic worth the search.
